=head1 DESCRIPTION

Configures the solutions' response sorting that enables partners to
order solutions based on specified attributes.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 B<REQUIRED> SortBy => Str

Specifies the attribute to sort by, such as C<Name>, C<CreatedDate>, or
C<Status>.


=head2 B<REQUIRED> SortOrder => Str

Specifies the sorting order, either C<Ascending> or C<Descending>. The
default is C<Descending>.



